data.description:
Welcome to this charming one and a half story home with four bedrooms and one bath, near the North Shoppes. 
As you approach the home, you'll notice its classic exterior featuring durable vinyl siding. The clean lines and low-maintenance materials not only enhance the home's curb appeal but also ensure long-lasting beauty. This expansive yard provides plenty of space for outdoor activities, gardening, and relaxation while offering a safe and secure environment for children and pets to roam freely.
The main level also houses three of the four bedrooms.  These bedrooms can also serve as home offices, guest rooms, or playrooms, depending on your needs. The single bathroom is conveniently located on the main level and features modern fixtures and finishes, ensuring your comfort and convenience.
One of the standout features of this property is the two-car detached garage, offering ample space for vehicle storage, entertaining, a workshop, or additional storage needs. Whether you have a passion for cars or simply need extra space for hobbies, this garage is sure to impress.
This one and a half story home with its large, fenced-in yard, vinyl siding, and two-car detached garage combines comfort, character, and functionality. It's a perfect canvas for creating lasting memories and enjoying the simple pleasures of home life. Don't miss the opportunity to make this delightful property your own.
